{"tid":1745452,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"區選劇本預測 + 焦土策略分析","createTime":"2019-11-22T08:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T10:56:26.000Z","uid":113277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"77ca9fa1d04213677674440ff66c0215399e8acb","tid":1745452,"uid":113277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:28:09.000Z","msg":"區選一定會選，呢個係國際形象工程，政府一定會攪。但係驚輸，點算？梗係又係派鬼啦。當前政府最想成個抗爭陣型內訌，最想和理非割蓆，同勇武互屌然後一齊灰心收皮。區選就係佢一個好好出招時機。<br />\n<br />\n一定有一大班和理非好想投票，又有一班焦土或者制度失效論覺得選票已經無意思。只要不斷挑撥呢個矛盾就好易互屌內訌。<br />\n選個日啲鬼會扮勇武，做最少既事例如阻路、遊行之類，咁政府就會立即宣佈選舉中止，並立即強烈譴責勇武。係鬼+政府+真心勇武煽風點火之下，雙方開始互屌，跟住重覆雨傘既結果。<br />\n<br />\n點樣先可避免？<br />\n<br />\n1. 和理非唔好覺得投左票就完，抗爭條路仲好長，唔好當前線係condom<br />\n<br />\n2. 勇武、焦土，你唔投就唔好投。投票個日咪休息一日囉，你抗爭多一日實際對成件事有咩幫助？<br />\n<br />\n最後講焦土。已方人員可以安全離開戰區（香港），而敵人不能在戰區中得到補給，就係真焦土。如果你離開唔到戰區，又俾彈藥（選票）敵人，咁你係資敵兼自殺，唔係焦土。"},{"pid":"df3c9ab381720f78192ce367feab4ed19f626265","tid":1745452,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:30:34.000Z","msg":"你抗爭多一日實際對成件事有咩幫助？<br />\n厲害厲害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91a9863cb005455813ccb7ce0f3d04b09f370d1","tid":1745452,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"**** 眾籌 ****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(由於中大民調欠缺資金做今次反送中民調，我們的眾籌會同時加入新項目，籌到的款項亦會用作資助中大民調)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先75%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持<br />\n<br />\n第六期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=b6ee4f99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=f8fa9a0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"b7f75b54874aba082ff71887373f84b3200c36a6","tid":1745452,"uid":113277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:59:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6ae29bafd0c450b40f8b2b39c81746d0c4b4b40","tid":1745452,"uid":113277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:10:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58367381682528e8fb43588925b255a2511379fb","tid":1745452,"uid":85190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"2019年仲有人信焦土撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d883a69fb47ff92037350d7c75cfaad08691540e","tid":1745452,"uid":312332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:55:21.000Z","msg":"仲未明政府咩玩法既人留意<br />\n<br />\n你200萬+1人上街，佢屈9你20萬人<br />\n你5個月黎示威，佢屈你一少撮人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你只能夠講你計唔準，但佢可以話你都唔準，口同鼻拗</span><br />\n但係今次區選當公投，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係實打實既數字</span><br />\n＜就算對方種票，佢都要有身份證，影響既只會係<span style=\"color: red;\">地區議席分布，而唔係黃藍人數</span>＞<br />\n440幾萬選民，唔可能變500萬張選票<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">宜家應該係煲大區選</span><br />\n   投建制派=支持止暴制亂<br />\n   投黃投獨立=沒有暴動，只有暴政<br />\n<br />\n結果一出黎<br />\n黃票多過200萬，政府<span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以再講一少撮人</span><br />\n藍票低過200萬，<span style=\"color: red;\">輪到我地屈佢一少撮人</span><br />\n<br />\n宜家係要煲大佢<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">   投建制派=支持止暴制亂 </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">  投黃投獨立=沒有暴動，只有暴政</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">選舉人數輸左=玻璃球打爛左</span><br />\n打爛左個玻璃球既後果係<br />\n1：運動失敗，逃亡潮開始<br />\n2：勇武轉化革命份子，引發更大暴力<br />\n3：香港政府管治失敗<br />\n<br />\n如果無更大暴力事件，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁你都輸得甘心命抵啦，仲唔快手著草</span><br />\n輸唔起就係你起革命，唔係逃避現實<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n咪發傻阻礙區選，比個位政府入<br />\n話你地一少撮人唔願意面對現實<br />\n<br />\n如果區選人頭黃多過藍，你仲可以反口話政府唔願面對現實，實實在在既數字啊<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n目標唔係含投<br />\n係要打倒建制派，無黃議員都要推假獨立<br />\n刷低對方明面上議席，清除舊有垃圾<br />\n新垃圾到時先諗計清，推到班假獨立起碼對方可以做25仔/牆頭草，唔係宜家一面倒垃圾建制派<br />\n<br />\n就算你唔覺得係公投，對家都會煲大佢變公投<br />\n先發制人<br />\n咁樣先可以動員更多港豬<br />\n<br />\n我幾個上年紀既同事仲發傻諗住唔投票<br />\n要同佢講對家會當今次係公投，先on99夢醒<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n無證無據話對方做假，大陸吹一堆假消息已經玩爛個真相<br />\n<br />\n中共外國超多打手玩假英文消息<br />\n<br />\n你要證明一件事有問題，就係要你舉出證據<br />\n否則只會當你自欺欺人<br />\n雖然信你既人會好多，但係外國佬無辦法直接插手，無證據點放上枱啊<br />\n<br />\n你今次煲大佢，<br />\n一係對方唔做手腳<br />\n黃票真係多，我地贏<br />\n<br />\n一係對方做手腳<br />\n我地/外國捉到對方做手腳，我地都贏<br />\n<br />\n捉唔到對方做手腳，就到時做文宣講選舉有問題啦<br />\n結果都係返到去，無證據，對方信定唔信<br />\n<br />\n點玩都咁被動，點解唔認真d投票"},{"pid":"e86548b2394fcad7b3df1ef4c32ded50709d0588","tid":1745452,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:56:14.000Z","msg":"嗰D唔係焦土派，而係熱狗<br />\n熱狗每逢選舉前就會出現，過去幾次選舉都係，又要派人𠝹票，又要叫人投白票，總之就係要保皇狗贏"},{"pid":"1f76a6e19b8324a56e05bb897194e8e6468e9f46","tid":1745452,"uid":251265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:56:38.000Z","msg":"企圖抹黑民主派，呼籲手足投白票一律視為共諜"},{"pid":"5eaaa277f278a2691153256f3a011999a156ee1b","tid":1745452,"uid":251265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e86548b2394fcad7b3df1ef4c32ded50709d0588","tid":1745452,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:56:14.000Z","msg":"嗰D唔係焦土派，而係熱狗<br />\n熱狗每逢選舉前就會出現，過去幾次選舉都係，又要派人𠝹票，又要叫人投白票，總之就係要保皇狗贏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:57:20.000Z","msg":"熱狗好明顯已經係共諜，係到維穩分化"},{"pid":"43e328b53c9ef8309acb1c1338b7d4f77ce4ff9a","tid":1745452,"uid":113277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e86548b2394fcad7b3df1ef4c32ded50709d0588","tid":1745452,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:56:14.000Z","msg":"嗰D唔係焦土派，而係熱狗<br />\n熱狗每逢選舉前就會出現，過去幾次選舉都係，又要派人𠝹票，又要叫人投白票，總之就係要保皇狗贏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:23:47.000Z","msg":"都費事開名啦，好簡單，開CY Leung Facebook 睇下佢寫啲文，hide 左個名似唔似熱青城陳雲啲文？你話佢地係唔係同一陣型？"},{"pid":"a709623e36985beb384a558f7023ede0ed136c32","tid":1745452,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:56:26.000Z","msg":"先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}